snippet.title: KIDS KILLING KIDS -- THE REAL PANDEMIC
snippet.description:
We must do something now!  Who will stand with me?  

School Assembly Info:
DestroyIllusionsTour.com

Follow on social media:
@TomCoverlyTour

About Tom Coverly:
TOM COVERLY is known as 'THE ILLUSIONIST'.  He is a professional comedian, illusionist and motivational speaker. Tom has spoken to over 4 million students around the world headlining several tours in the past two decades. He is one of the most requested motivational entertainers in the nation. 

Tom has been seen on TV (ABC, NBC, FOX, Access Hollywood) & heard on numerous radio stations around the country sharing his story. He has entertained several celebrities, Jep & Jessica Robertson from the hit TV show,

"Duck Dynasty", Cast of C.S.I. NY, Alec Mapa (Desperate Housewives & Ugly Betty), Rick the Reptile Guy (A&E TV Show, "WildTransport"), Amber Montana (Nickelodeon TV show "Haunted Hathaways"), Victoria Koloff (Lifetime TV show, “Preachers’ Daughters”), i-Shine TV (TBN) & entertained the entire cast and producers for the "Batman Vs. Superman" Movie.  
 
Tom has performed for major corporations like; Warner Brothers, Gerber, Amway, Sprint, Arby's & Burger King just to name a few. He has shared the stage with many of the nations most recognized music acts; Skillet, Brian "Head" of Korn, Toby Mac, Thompson Square, NF, Lacrae, SwitchFoot, Danny Gokey (American Idol), Newsboys, Pop Evil and many more!
